## Test: TestHashIDsNClones

### Purpose
Verify that N clones can work offline and sync without ID collisions using hash IDs.

### Test Scenario
```
Setup:
- 1 bare remote repo
- 5 clones (A, B, C, D, E)

Offline Work:
- Each clone creates 10 issues with different titles
- No coordination, no network access
- Total: 50 unique issues

Sync:
- Clones sync in random order
- Each pull/import other clones' issues

Expected Result:
- All 5 clones converge to 50 issues
- Zero ID collisions
- Zero remapping needed
- Alias conflicts resolved deterministically
```

### Implementation
File: cmd/bd/beads_hashid_test.go (new)

```go
func TestHashIDsFiveClones(t *testing.T) {
    tmpDir := t.TempDir()
    remoteDir := setupBareRepo(t, tmpDir)

    // Setup 5 clones
    clones := make(map[string]string)
    for _, name := range []string{"A", "B", "C", "D", "E"} {
        clones[name] = setupClone(t, tmpDir, remoteDir, name)
    }

    // Each clone creates 10 issues offline
    for name, dir := range clones {
        for i := 0; i < 10; i++ {
            createIssue(t, dir, fmt.Sprintf("%s-issue-%d", name, i))
        }
        // No sync yet!
    }

    // Sync in random order
    syncOrder := []string{"C", "A", "E", "B", "D"}
    for _, name := range syncOrder {
        syncClone(t, clones[name], name)
    }

    // Final convergence round
    for _, name := range []string{"A", "B", "C", "D", "E"} {
        finalPull(t, clones[name], name)
    }

    // Verify all clones have all 50 issues
    for name, dir := range clones {
        issues := getIssues(t, dir)
        if len(issues) != 50 {
            t.Errorf("Clone %s: expected 50 issues, got %d", name, len(issues))
        }

        // Verify all issue IDs are hash-based
        for _, issue := range issues {
            if !strings.HasPrefix(issue.ID, "bd-") || len(issue.ID) != 11 {
                t.Errorf("Invalid hash ID: %s", issue.ID)
            }
        }
    }

    // Verify no collision resolution occurred
    // (This would be in logs if it happened)

    t.Log("✓ All 5 clones converged to 50 issues with zero collisions")
}
```

